title: Cut the Body Loose
text:
Cut the Body Loose is the fifth solo studio album by American hip hop artist <a href="Astronautalis">Astronautalis</a>. It was released via <a href="SideOneDummy%20Records">SideOneDummy Records</a> on May 13, 2016. Music videos were created for "Sike!", "Running Away from God", and "Kurt Cobain". In the week of April 22, 2016, "<a href="Consequence%20of%20Sound">Consequence of Sound</a>" placed "Attila Ambrus" at number 8 on the "Top 10 Songs of the Week" list.
Personnel.
Credits adapted from liner notes.
